ze-joaquin-phoenix-scarlett-johansson","author":{"fullName":"Sheon Han"},"uid":"Entry:6692a09c-7b1a-48c3-9aa5-cd3950f24d49"}}]},{"heading":"In the News","entries":[{"title":"","entry":{"title":"OpenAI introduces Sora, its text-to-video AI model","promoHeadline":null,"uuid":"069653a7-904f-42c7-82a4-f89f6e8a61e0","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/15/24074151/openai-sora-text-to-video-ai","author":{"fullName":"Emma Roth"},"uid":"Entry:069653a7-904f-42c7-82a4-f89f6e8a61e0"}},{"title":"","entry":{"title":"Apple is reportedly working on AI updates to Spotlight and Xcode","promoHeadline":null,"uuid":"51e82de4-a567-48a7-8999-3705b5146570","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/15/24074455/apple-generative-ai-xcode-spotlight-testing","author":{"fullName":"Emilia David"},"uid":"Entry:51e82de4-a567-48a7-8999-3705b5146570"}},{"title":"","entry":{"title":"Gemini Advanced is most impressive when it’s working with Google","promoHeadline":null,"uuid":"ca095f64-ec5f-4200-aa6a-76c1e6441e1e","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/14/24066552/google-openai-gemini-ultra-chatgpt-chatbots","author":{"fullName":"Emilia David"},"uid":"Entry:ca095f64-ec5f-4200-aa6a-76c1e6441e1e"}},{"title":"","entry":{"title":"Slack AI is here, letting you catch up on lengthy threads and unread messages","promoHeadline":null,"uuid":"2cba6487-dde1-4414-997e-d1556cb79444","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/14/24070590/slack-ai-launch-thread-summaries-search-recap","author":{"fullName":"Emma Roth"},"uid":"Entry:2cba6487-dde1-4414-997e-d1556cb79444"}},{"title":"","entry":{"title":"ChatGPT is getting ‘memory’ to remember who you are and what you like","promoHeadline":null,"uuid":"d5a728f5-268f-4a44-82f1-9d20e0c3eef5","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/13/24071106/chatgpt-memory-openai-ai-chatbot-history","author":{"fullName":"David Pierce"},"uid":"Entry:d5a728f5-268f-4a44-82f1-9d20e0c3eef5"}},{"title":"","entry":{"title":"Semafor reporters are going to curate the news with AI","promoHeadline":null,"u